            <head xml:id="zef3dd-d1e520-Hd1e101">Caput 27</head>
            <head xml:id="zef3dd-d1e520-Hd1e103" type="question-title">De Scripturae definitione</head>
            <p xml:id="zef3dd-d1e520-d1e106">
               <lb ed="#B" n="84"/>CAPUT XXVII 
<lb ed="#B" n="85"/>ET ULTIMUM. 
      <lb ed="#B" n="86"/>DE SCRIPTURAE DEFINITIONE, 
      </p>
            <p xml:id="zef3dd-d1e520-d1e115">
               <lb ed="#B" n="87"/>539. Definitio Scripturae sacrae potest tradi 
      <lb ed="#B" n="88"/>jusmodi: Sacra Scriptura est verbum Dei ejusdem 
      <lb ed="#B" n="89"/>voluntate a prophetis, evangelistis et apostolis in 
      <lb ed="#B" n="90"/>literas redactum, doctrinam de essentia et voluntate 
      <lb ed="#B" n="91"/>Dei perfecte ac perspicue exponens, ut ex eo 
      homi<lb ed="#B" n="92" break="no"/>nes erudiantur ad vitam aeternam. Conserva e 
      <lb ed="#B" n="93"/>anctifica nos, Deus, in veritate tua, cermo tuus ve 
      <lb ed="#B" n="94"/>rilas est, Joh. 17, v. 17. Amen. 
</p>
         </div>
